Package com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection

Class Field

java.lang.Object
com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection.Member
com.telenav.kivakit.core.language.reflection.Field
public class Field extends Member
Provides access to a field of a particular object, or of any object.

Field Access

  • get() - Reads this field's value on any object passed to the constructor
  • get(Object) - Reads this field's value on the given object
  • makeAccessible() - Makes the field accessible even if it is private
  • object(Object) - Sets the object to access when calling get() and set(Object)
  • set(Object) - Writes the given value to this field of any object passed to the constructor
  • set(Object, Object) - Writes the given value to this field of the given object
  • type() - Returns the type of this field

  • annotation(Class)
  • Member.hasAnnotation(Class)
